                    id: "about-me-img",
                    style: "border-radius:50%; width:50%; margin-top:10px;") %>

      <p>
        I am a passionate developer who focuses their studies in
        computer graphics programming. It is the grand scope and
        challenge that drives me forward in understanding how to
