        and The Expanse by James S. A. Corey. <br><br>

        If you wish to learn more about me and my technical interest, please check out my,
        <strong><%= link_to("Projects", projects_path) %></strong> and
        <strong><%= link_to("Articles", articles_path) %></strong>. <br><br>

        Take care and happy coding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
